Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs-3\shad0\bord3\be20\3c&HD30BDF&\pos(1063.2,546.2)}Rule Number 10
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的~
